extendedInfo.description: Join over 400 professionals at the equity compensation industry's signature event. Here you can engage in a broad mix of interactive sessions with expert theorists and practitioners. Take this opportunity to delve into critical topics in reporting practices, trends, international challenges, employee communication, and much more. You'll leave Carlsbad energized and equipped with actionable strategies to help you attract, retain, and reward the world's top talent.App Keywords Directions, Directions 2013, Annual Conference, Carlsbad.
